Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================OP============================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.82,0:02:33.81,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}茫茫人海行色匆匆　擦肩而过碰撞纠缠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.01,0:02:39.93,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}感受彼此羽翼的伤痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:46.12,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}用寂寞抱紧你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:52.57,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}无须其他任何表示
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:55.94,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}等候交融的瞬间　觉醒的永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:58.99,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}心急如焚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.46,0:03:05.52,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}时光荏苒转瞬即逝　
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.69,0:03:14.99,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}只能叹息　心愿遥不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:21.29,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}炽热的灵魂　传递真情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:24.49,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}不再有保留
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.65,0:03:30.84,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}你曾经的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.59,0:03:36.12,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}又在何方…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================ED============================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.22,0:22:11.85,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,1500)}曾如此形影不离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:20.94,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,2500)}黄昏却已变色…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.72,0:22:37.28,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}平凡的温柔　让你远去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.53,0:22:45.01,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}被抛弃的心灵　四处彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.33,0:22:53.24,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}这份失落　如果就是生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:57.52,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}我愿在夜空下　从此闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:06.55,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}曾形影不离　黄昏却已变色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.80,0:23:17.77,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}{\be1}至少让我在月光下　静静入眠…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Avant============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.22,0:00:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C.E.70年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「血色情人节」的悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.81,0:00:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导致地球与PLANT的紧张关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.32,0:00:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终升级为武力冲突
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.05,0:00:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战前无人怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.86,0:00:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球军将以数量优势取胜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.72,0:00:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是　现实出乎所有人的预料
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.14,0:00:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战局陷入拉锯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转眼 第十一个月即将过去…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.31,0:00:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.17,0:00:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.41,0:01:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到驾驶座后面去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.94,0:01:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩这一架
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.60,0:01:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我至少要把它开出去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.18,0:01:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.51,0:01:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高…达？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Main============================
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:50.06,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1170,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord3\shad1\be20\an3\fs60}其名高达
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.34,0:03:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赫利奥波利斯全域发布八级避难警报
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请居民尽快就近前往避难中心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.41,0:04:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉斯提失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.97,0:04:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.66,0:04:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对面的机体上　坐的是地球军士官
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.32,0:04:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛 多尔 卡兹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.85,0:04:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去捉那架机体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.23,0:04:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你带着这东西先撤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.07,0:04:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.55,0:04:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不可能在那种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开！想死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.39,0:05:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.92,0:05:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.59,0:05:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这机动战士…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西…怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.34,0:05:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的装甲是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们配备的是相转移装甲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦启动 Ginn的军刀伤不了它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.43,0:06:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还不快走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.39,0:06:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磨磨蹭蹭干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.62,0:06:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管你装甲多好…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的机动性…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不自量力了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.00,0:06:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然人也玩机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.82,0:07:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面还有平民
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.68,0:07:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然坐在这东西里 就想点办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.61,0:07:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太胡闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这样的OS 控制这么复杂的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没全部完成呢 没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.48,0:07:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.46,0:07:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.05,0:08:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.06,0:08:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校准同时重设零力矩点&CPG
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 那就让控制模块直控分子态离子泵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重筑神经末梢网络
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更新原始参数
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复前馈控制 传送函数！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.07,0:08:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调整克里奥利偏差
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.93,0:08:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接通运动常态
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系统上线 引导程序启动！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.22,0:08:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作突然变快了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.45,0:08:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:08:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再就是…「破甲者」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.95,0:08:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这个吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死 到处乱窜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.03,0:09:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在这种地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.51,0:09:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氢系统失去响应
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.24,0:09:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舷驱动当机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 离开Ginn
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船！ 大天使号呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去控制！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 这兵力差距
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无能为力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥罗尔机重创 紧急返航
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消防班 B甲板待命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.98,0:10:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥罗尔机体重创？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.01,0:10:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种战斗里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎有只烦人的苍蝇在飞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到米歇尔·艾曼的激光信号
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急状态
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连米歇尔也失去了机体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的一架 不能放过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.42,0:11:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗 还有人活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有幸存者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.81,0:11:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴基露露少尉 你没事就好！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 还有什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:11:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我感觉到你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.02,0:12:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也感觉到我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.02,0:12:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不幸的宿缘啊 穆·拉·弗拉戈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.07,0:12:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先别起来为好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.83,0:12:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自作主张…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.95,0:12:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.10,0:12:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊 这架「高达」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.18,0:12:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能开动吗 行不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩个 别乱摆弄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.65,0:13:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么又变回灰色的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是主电池干了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那上面下来！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他们 把昏迷的你抬下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你们出手相救
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.02,0:13:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是军队的重要机密
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.47,0:13:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是平民可以随便碰的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.36,0:13:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 刚才不是基拉在驾驶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.76,0:13:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依次报上姓名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛·阿盖尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.71,0:13:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡兹·巴斯卡克
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多尔·凯尼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:13:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米丽雅莉娅·霍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉·大和
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫玛硫·拉米亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.94,0:14:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是地球联邦军的士官
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.52,0:14:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常遗憾 我不能放你们原地解散了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.57,0:14:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论出于何种原因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目睹了军方重要机密的你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.91,0:14:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我和相关方面取得联系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并收到处理决定前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须留在我的监视范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.49,0:14:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.90,0:14:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们必须服从我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.51,0:14:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是赫利奥波利斯的居民！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是中立的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和军队什么的 没一丝一毫关系！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底 地球军为什么会在赫利奥波利斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.59,0:14:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们才有问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.02,0:14:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 所以才把这里糟蹋成这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:14:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.14,0:15:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无知的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.91,0:15:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为宣称中立 宣称与己无关
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能继续置身事外
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会真的这么想吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有地球军的重要机密
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.54,0:15:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你们必须面对的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太粗暴了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管粗暴不粗暴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是战争
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.81,0:15:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PLANT和地球的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调整人和自然人的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.23,0:15:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在外面的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是 劳·卢·克鲁泽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.94,0:15:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是这么碍事 穆·拉·弗拉戈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.94,0:16:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想你对我也有同感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.10,0:16:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去赫利奥波利斯里了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.47,0:16:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有爆炸时离船的少数几人生还
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.83,0:16:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大多是工人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.73,0:16:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战况如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎夫特舰船在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们忙于确认身边情况
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是大天使号
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.21,0:16:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的爆炸无法击沉它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 港内的瓦砾堆积严重
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.62,0:16:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们完全被困死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通讯干扰还在继续 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 这里是佯攻？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.04,0:16:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎夫特的目标是曙光社！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 那边现在什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「G」到底怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.13,0:17:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里… 105强袭…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球军… 回答…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.72,0:17:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是X105强袭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.75,0:17:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球军 请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.27,0:17:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球军 请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5号拖车 是那辆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.25,0:17:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.72,0:17:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.22,0:17:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来呢 我们该做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取出强袭者能量包
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.21,0:17:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 基拉再试着联系一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.12,0:17:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种地形…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能就此消失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会十分高兴 穆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.35,0:18:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现有人手 就算出击也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有说话的功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如去考虑如何启动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曙光社也许还在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道继续躲在这里 对外面不闻不问吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.78,0:18:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带他们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到座位上去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.86,0:18:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按电脑指示操作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.69,0:18:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面还有扎夫特舰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.06,0:18:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们应付不了战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动舰船的同时 准备发射特装炮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.90,0:18:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到吧 上士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.12,0:18:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入启航程序
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.05,0:18:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况紧急 省略C-30到L-21的步骤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.56,0:19:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主动力系统 上线
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功率输出稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离到达额定值 450秒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.78,0:19:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.35,0:19:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认和赫利奥波利斯的连接情况
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.90,0:19:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完好！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.24,0:19:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那里获取能量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开通导管
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.43,0:19:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把能量与累加器接通
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.56,0:19:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认接通 输出正常 距离额定值20秒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.54,0:19:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维生装置 正常
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.91,0:19:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}C　I　C　　　\N{\fs44}战斗指挥室上线
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.45,0:19:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器系统 上线
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}　　　F C S\N{\fs44}接通火控
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磁场控制室 以及配弹室运行正常
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外部装甲减震器 最大功率
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.55,0:19:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主动力满负荷 引擎正常
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.00,0:19:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号全系统上线
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.34,0:19:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关闭气压阀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.14,0:19:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员准备应对冲击和突发性舰体破损
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:19:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢速前进 大天使号出发
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量包是哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器和能量包是一体的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.58,0:20:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接装备上去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.68,0:20:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避难命令还没解除
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.36,0:20:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸老妈不知道有没有去避难
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.84,0:20:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 好想早点回家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.94,0:21:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动战士！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.94,0:21:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 就是它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的一架吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.66,0:21:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安上装备 快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.86,0:21:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.82,0:21:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斩草就要除根
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.06,0:21:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特装炮发射同时 最高战速
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.42,0:22:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Next============================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.18,0:23:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为保护友人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.65,0:23:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竭尽全力与敌人战斗的基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.66,0:23:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是射出的炮火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.59,0:23:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会诉说他的善良
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.00,0:23:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑洞洞的枪口与枪口之间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.56,0:23:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有生死与憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.45,0:23:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年们被迫重新审视
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.35,0:23:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扣下扳机的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.40,0:23:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 机动战士高达SEED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.86,0:23:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「分崩离析的大地」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.51,0:23:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击退眼前的威胁 高达


